                     <interp inst="t18310630-279-person2008" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am shopman to 
               <persName id="t18310630-279-person2009">
                  James 
                  Veitch
               <interp inst="t18310630-279-person2009" type="surname" value="Veitch"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310630-279-person2009" type="given" value="James"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18310630-279-person2009" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , a <rs id="t18310630-279-viclabel1459" type="occupation">linen<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183106300128"></xptr>draper</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310630-279-victim2004 t18310630-279-viclabel1459"></join>. This print is my master's, and measures twentyfour yards.</p>
               <p>Clark's Defence. I was looking for work - I saw this print on the ground, and the Policeman stopped me.</p>
               <p>Woodruft's Defence. I was in company with nobody, and had never seen Clark.</p>
